Class IDataSharedCursorEnvelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • permafrost.tundra.data.IDataSharedCursorEnvelope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.data.IDataSharedCursor, com.wm.txn.ITransactionResource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CopyOnWriteIDataMap.CopyOnWriteIDataSharedCursor

    public class IDataSharedCursorEnvelope
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.wm.data.IDataSharedCursor
    Wraps an IDataSharedCursor in an envelope object and provides a skeletal implementation for subclasses.
